\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"JAAA\", \"from\": 148, \"to\": 152}, {\"ngram\": \"just 14 team officials\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 176}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mills also said that he has received offers to be a member of other nations' delegations for the Games and if forced, he may consider his options.\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mills\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 256}, {\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 294}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"other nations' delegations\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 339}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"his options\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is a disgrace that the Jamaica Olympic Association denies track and field the benefit of the required numbers,\\\" Mills said.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamaica Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Olympic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disgrace\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"the benefit\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"the required numbers\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"Mills\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Seventeen persons for a team of 65-70 athletes is totally inadequate.\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Seventeen persons\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 545}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"65-70 athletes\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know that and I have been there and I have done that.\\\"\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mills, formerly the coach of Jamaica's sprint legend Usain Bolt, said that he had declined offers from two other Olympic associations to join their team for this year's Olympic Games due to his love for his country.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999998599378, \"rank\": 1.398731467352686e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mills\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"formerly the coach\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 753}, {\"ngram\": \"two other Olympic associations\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"their team\", \"from\": 798, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Olympic Games\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"his love\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"his country\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If it is forced that I recognise the necessity for other coaches who have numerous athletes, I could have gone to the Olympics with other countries,\\\" Mills said.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the necessity\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"other coaches\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous athletes\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"other countries\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"Mills\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was offered two full accreditations, full funding, but I could never see myself wearing another country's [colours], but if I am forced to, then I will have to.\\\"\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two full accreditations\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"full funding\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"another country\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"colours\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mills has been involved in nine previous Olympic Games as part of Jamaica's technical and coaching staff.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1268, \"end\": 1275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999998599378, \"rank\": 1.398731467352686e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mills\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"nine previous Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that he is dismayed at the JOA's decision to limit the JAAA to 14 team officials for the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1343, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JOA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\"}, {\"begin\": 1371, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JAAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"14 team officials\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I find it very unfortunate that track and field, and what it represents in the Olympic movement, not just in Jamaica but worldwide, along with Jamaica's history, we are not beggars, we have earned it,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999998599378, \"rank\": 1.398731467352686e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 1566, \"end\": 1573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999998599378, \"rank\": 1.398731467352686e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that track\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic movement\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"beggars\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been to nine Olympics.\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nine Olympics\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a disgrace that you have to fight to get the required number of coaches, the required number of therapists and doctors to go with an Olympic team that is probably rated number two or three in the world.\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disgrace\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"the required number\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"the required number\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"therapists\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"doctors\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic team\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"number\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have done six or seven Olympics as the technical director and coach, so I know what it is to go there and work with so many different events and so many responsibilities.\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 2048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six or seven Olympics\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"the technical director\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"coach\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1945}, {\"ngram\": \"so many different events\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2018}, {\"ngram\": \"so many responsibilities\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I cannot see why the number is a problem.\\\"\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"JAAA President Garth Gayle explained that they have made it clear to the JOA that the 14 spots allocated are insufficient.\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2097, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JAAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2118, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"score\": 0.9999901058136571, \"rank\": 9.8942822807493e-06, \"text\": \"Gayle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\"}, {\"begin\": 2170, \"end\": 2173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JOA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 14 spots\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He expressed disappointment over not receiving a response despite requesting a review.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"disappointment\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2247}, {\"ngram\": \"a response\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"a review\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gayle underscored the necessity for additional personnel, including medical staff, therapists, and management, to adequately support athletes across various disciplines at next month's Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gayle\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"the necessity\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"additional personnel\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2363}, {\"ngram\": \"medical staff\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"therapists\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"management\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"various disciplines\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"next month's Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe this is a reasonable request,\\\" Gayle said in a press conference on Monday.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2551, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"score\": 0.9999901058136571, \"rank\": 9.8942822807493e-06, \"text\": \"Gayle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a reasonable request\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"a press conference\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2583}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Considering the wide range of disciplines, horizontal jumps, vertical jumps, throws, as well as medical personnel and therapists, we are requesting the JOA to increase the number by three to make it 17.\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2748, \"end\": 2751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JOA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wide range\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"disciplines\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"horizontal jumps\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"vertical jumps\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2671}, {\"ngram\": \"throws\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2679}, {\"ngram\": \"medical personnel\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"therapists\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Their response has been 14 and that's it, but we are asking that they review it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their response\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When contacted on Monday, JOA President Christopher Samuda said he would provide a factual response at a later date.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 3000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2910, \"end\": 2913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JOA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newspaper_Preservation_Act_of_1970\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2908}, {\"ngram\": \"a factual response\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2983}, {\"ngram\": \"a later date\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 2999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3015}]}]}"